sentences: Warren Fu is an American music video director, illustrator and designer.

He has directed promos for Daft Punk, The Weeknd, Snoop Dogg, Pharrell Williams, The Strokes, HAIM, The Killers, Depeche Mode, Weezer, Paramore, Hayley Williams, Mark Ronson, Julian Casablancas, A Tribe Called Quest and Aaliyah.
Fu is signed to Partizan Entertainment worldwide for commercials and music videos, and Creative Artists Agency for feature films.
Fu was also responsible for designing General Grievous' concept art in the Star Wars prequels.
